=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldDiabetesDay\"><strong>#WorldDiabetesDay<br />\n</strong></a><strong>15:\u00a0</strong><strong><a href=\"https://www.timeanddate.com/holidays/un/world-philosophy-day\">World Philosophy Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldPhilosophyDay\">#WorldPhilosophyDay</a><br />\n</strong><strong>16:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/toleranceday/\">International Day for Tolerance</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/ToleranceDay\"><strong>#ToleranceDay</strong></a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23ToleranceDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>19: </strong><strong><a href=\"http://www.worldpancreaticcancerday.org/\">World Pancreatic Cancer Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WPCD20\">#WPCD20</a></strong><br />\n<strong>19:\u00a0<a href=\"http://worldtoilet.org/\">World Toilet Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldToiletDay\">#WorldToiletDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23WorldDiabetesDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>20: <a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/world-childrens-day\">World Children\u2019s Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0</strong><strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldChildrensDay\">#WorldChildrensDay</a></strong><strong><br />\n</strong><strong>21:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/events/televisionday/\">World Television Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldTVDay\">#WorldTVDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search/realtime?q=%23ChildrensDay\"><br />\n</a><strong>25:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/endviolenceday/\">International Day for the Elimination of Violence Against Women</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/EndViolenceAgainstWomen\">#EndViolenceAgainstWomen</a><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23EndViolenceAgainstWomen\"><br />\n</a></strong></p>\n<h2><strong>December</strong></h2>\n<p><strong>1: <a href=\"http://givingtuesday.org/\">Giving Tuesday</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/GivingTuesday\">#GivingTuesday</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>1:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\">World AIDS Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldAIDSDay\">#WorldAIDSDay</a><br />\n3:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.idpwd.com.au/\">International Day of People with Disabilities</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/IDPwD20\">#IDPwD20</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IDPWD\"><br />\n</a><strong>5:\u00a0<a href=\"https://www.un.org/en/observances/volunteer-day\">International Volunteer Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/VolunteerDay\">#VolunteerDay<br />\n</a>5:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/soilday/\">World Soil Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/WorldSoilDay\">#WorldSoilDay</a></strong><a href=\"https://twitter.com/search?q=%23IVD2014\"><br />\n</a><strong>9:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/anticorruptionday/\">International Anti-Corruption Day\u00a0</a>\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/AntiCorruptionDay\">#AntiCorruptionDay</a></strong><a href=\"http://www.worldaidsday.org/\"><br />\n</a><strong>10:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.ohchr.org/EN/AboutUs/Pages/HumanRightsDay.aspx\">International Human Rights Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/HumanRightsDay\">#HumanRightsDay</a></strong><br />\n<strong>11:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/mountainday/\">International Mountain Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MountainDay\">#MountainDay<br />\n</a>18:\u00a0<a href=\"http://www.un.org/en/events/migrantsday/\">International Migrants Day</a>\u00a0\u2014\u00a0<a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/MigrantsDay\">#MigrantsDay</a></strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p><span style=\"color: #c30437;\"><a style=\"color: #c30437;\" href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices-for-nonprofits/\"><em><strong>101 Best Practices for Nonprofits</strong></em></a></span> is a year-long blog and webinar series (written and presented by <span style=\"color: #c30437;\"><strong><a style=\"color: #c30437;\" href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/heather-mansfield/\">Heather Mansfield</a></strong></span>) on website design, email marketing, online fundraising, and social media best practices for nonprofits, NGOs, and charities worldwide. Sign up for\u00a0<a href=\"https://mailchi.mp/nptechforgood/news\"><strong><span style=\"color: #c30437;\">Nonprofit Tech for Good\u2019s email newsletter</span></strong></a>\u00a0to be alerted of new posts.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.nptechforgood.com/101-best-practices-for-nonprofits/\"><img data-recalc-dims=\"1\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-25066\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=960%2C480\" alt=\"\" width=\"960\" height=\"480\" srcset=\"https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?w=1200&amp;ssl=1 1200w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=300%2C150&amp;ssl=1 300w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=1024%2C512&amp;ssl=1 1024w, https://i0.wp.com/www.nptechforgood.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/1200-x-600-Banner.png?resize=768%2C384&amp;ssl=1 768w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\" /></a></p>\n",
